            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a full kettle</p><p>While the mushrooms are cooking, peel and chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved potatoes</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 10-12 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once the potatoes are fork-tender, drain them in a colander and shake them until they're fluffy</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1665139835776-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1665139835776-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
