            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, roughly chop your <strong>pistachios</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your<strong> green lentils</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained lentils</strong>, <strong>dried cranberries</strong>,<strong> chopped pistachios</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong>,<strong> half</strong> your <strong>dried sage</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>soy sauce</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to the onion and mushroom pan</p><p>Give everything a good mix up then roughly mash – this is your <strong>pistachio</strong> <strong>nut roast mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1665139839196-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
